{"id":316913,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/维权网-薛国平在搬迁指挥部被打，维权人士前往/","date":"2013-10-08T01:48:42Z","modified":"2013-10-08T01:48:42Z","title":"维权网 | 薛国平在搬迁指挥部被打，维权人士前往医院探望（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><span><span></span></span><br /><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><br /><span><span>（维权网信息员张宁宁报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>3</span></span><span>日，山东倪文华与张家港拆迁受害人以及当地维权人士前往如皋人民医院看望薛国平和其母亲。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span> <span lang=\"EN-US\"><span></span></span><br /></span><br /><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>20</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>13</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>9</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>25</span></span><span>日，如皋市龙游河村商务区拆迁指挥部的其工作人员到薛国平开烟花爆竹店内寻衅滋事。薛国平的亲属怕引爆烟花爆竹而发生意外，多次向</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>110</span></span><span>报警。民警姗姗来迟，不处理问题，反而要求大家到该搬迁指挥部去解决问题。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\n<p></span><span><span>到了该指挥部，双方发生了争执。薛国平被该指挥部工作人员殴打致伤。薛国平满脸是血，不省人事，薛国平的母亲也被打得骨折，同时送往如皋人民医院抢救。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span><br /><span><span></span><br /><span>薛国平住院已经有一个星期了。如今，薛国平还不能回忆当时的情景，失去记忆的症状十分明显。倪文华对薛国平的亲属说，向公安机关申请伤残程度鉴定，追究打人凶手的法律责任；并指出搬迁指挥部原是个不伦不类的东西。搬迁必须出于自愿，而该指挥部却有强制搬迁的权力。也是说，搬迁指挥部要强制居民自愿搬迁。这在逻辑上说不通，更无法律依据。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><br />  <span></span><br /><span>薛国平妻子季冬梅的手机号码：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>13773800128</span></span></span><br /><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span></span></span></p>\n<div>\n<div><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-hsR2TgAnQBM/UlNO5Ra2L1I/AAAAAAAApLM/pjKazXnmmW4/s1600/%E9%92%B11.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-hsR2TgAnQBM/UlNO5Ra2L1I/AAAAAAAApLM/pjKazXnmmW4/s320/%E9%92%B11.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-25OPT72wU84/UlNO7KSS_tI/AAAAAAAApLU/ZWqmNT23e8E/s1600/%E9%92%B1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-25OPT72wU84/UlNO7KSS_tI/AAAAAAAApLU/ZWqmNT23e8E/s320/%E9%92%B1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}